@ThinkingandTinkering I hear what you are saying and I see how it could come off that way, it's definitely about how you ask. 

If I made that for you though I would jump at the opportunity to animate it if you were going to use it as your intro on your channel.

Then everytime I play a new video I'd get to see my contribution but hey that's my opinion. Other really popular youtubers are exclusively hosting fan made intros and it's a beautiful symbiotic thing.
